Package: ZinaSuite
Title: A Modern R Package for UCSC Xena Data Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Shixiang",
           family = "Wang",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "w_shixiang@163.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9855-7357"))
Description: Provides a modernized framework for interactively exploring
    UCSC Xena datasets. It enables downloading, analyzing and visualizing
    datasets from UCSC Xena with enhanced performance through mirai-based
    asynchronous computing and modular Shiny application design.
    The package supports TCGA, PCAWG, and CCLE datasets with advanced
    molecular analysis capabilities including correlation, survival,
    mutation, and immune analysis.
